  "title": "Sales Advisor (Retail - Hair Wig) | CBD | Basic + Allowance + Commission",
  "description": "<p><strong>Working Days: 5 Days (Rotating Shifts)</strong><br>\n<strong>Working Hours: Up to 44 hours per week</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3><strong>Job Description:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Customer Interaction:</strong> Demonstrate excellent communication skills with customers, understanding their needs and preferences.</li>\n  <li><strong>Sales &amp; Fitting:</strong> Assist customers in selecting wigs, fitting, and styling them to meet their expectations.</li>\n  <li><strong>Wig Care &amp; Styling Advice:</strong> Provide personalized advice to customers on wig care and home-styling techniques.</li>\n  <li><strong>Hairpiece Maintenance:</strong> Maintain and style hairpieces under the guidance of the Hair Stylist Director, ensuring top-notch service.</li>\n  <li><strong>Product Display &amp; Standards:</strong> Ensure that all products and displays maintain the highest level of customer satisfaction.</li>\n  <li><strong>Training:</strong> Receive product and maintenance training from the Hair Stylist Director to enhance your skills.</li>\n  <li><strong>Additional Duties:</strong> Perform other duties as required by the Hair Stylist Director to support the salon's operations.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements:</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum of 2 years of experience in the retail industry.</li>\n  <li><strong>Bonus:</strong> Proficiency in hair styling will be an added advantage, with an additional allowance.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Choo Sian<br>\nEA Personnel No: R1762582<br>\nEA License No: 23C1703</p>",
